    <div class="eq">
      <div class="eq-lbl">Cinética y parámetros de diseño (T = 800°C)</div>
      C₂H₆  →  C₂H₄  +  H₂     (ΔHrx = +137 kJ/mol, irreversible a 800°C)<br>
      k(T) = 4.65×10¹³ · exp(−272,000 / (R·T))   [s⁻¹]<br>
      k(800°C)  ≈ 2.29 s⁻¹<br>
      τ_PFR  = −ln(1−0.60)/k = 0.400 s = 400 ms<br>
